AMPIRE CO LTD (8049)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 3.84% to NT$103,821,000 from NT$107,967,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            103,821          107,967    
YOY%              -3.84%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            385,966          390,896    
YOY%              -1.26% 
=================================================================
 